snippet.title: TEALERLAND Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to TEALERLAND. https://gamejolt.com/games/TEALERLAND/466109

1/14/2021 Note: This was the game's first trailer, and the gameplay shown in it is a little bit outdated. More recent trailers along with the game page show gameplay footage that is much more closer to what is seen in the demo and full game.

(Music: 'Desertion' by Bonnot on Newgrounds https://www.newgrounds.com/audio/listen/892125, VHS static from ANFX)
